        <p class="i18n" data-lang="zh">循环关系探测评估通过单选题测试视觉语言模型的关系理解能力,涵盖主体、谓词和客体元素。包含 4 个分割评估物体识别和空间关系理解,含异常/罕见关系。</p>
      
<div class="bench-stat-badges"><span class="bench-stat-badge"><span class="i18n" data-lang="en">2,000 images</span><span class="i18n" data-lang="zh">2,000 张图片</span></span><span class="bench-stat-badge"><span class="i18n" data-lang="en">2,000 questions</span><span class="i18n" data-lang="zh">2,000 个问题</span></span></div>
